snippet.title: Menace from the Deep - Demo Launch Trailer. Play demo on Steam at Feb 2024
snippet.description:
Finishing the demo of my project Menace from the Deep. It is a roguelike deckbuilding game in a Lovecraft inspired world. 

Please add to wishlist to make the full version game to release one day.
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2644610/Menace_from_the_Deep/?l=ukrainian
